---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import ContactForm from '../components/ContactForm.tsx';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <main>
    <Hero />
    
    <!-- Problem-Solution Section 1: Sistemas de Venta e Inventario -->
    <section id="servicios" class="py-20 md:py-28 px-6 bg-background border-t border-border">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="mb-14">
          <p class="badge text-accent mb-4">Sistemas de venta e inventario</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-balance mb-4">
            Apps de pago que no terminan de convencerte
          </h2>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground max-w-lg text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
            Desarrollo un sistema a tu medida: punto de venta, control de inventario, corte de caja, clientes.
            Es un desarrollo completo, por lo que se maneja con pago mensual e incluye soporte.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="group bg-card border border-border rounded-xl p-6 md:p-7 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-black/[0.02] hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"/><path d="M12 9v4"/><path d="M10 11h4"/><path d="M6 16h12"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-1.5">Sistemas de venta e inventario</h3>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
                  &iquest;Usas una app de pago que no termina de convencerte? Te construyo un sistema
                  a tu medida: punto de venta, control de inventario, corte de caja, clientes.
                  Es un desarrollo completo, por lo que se maneja con pago mensual e incluye soporte.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
                  <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground bg-secondary px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md">Pago mensual</span>
                  <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground bg-secondary px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md">Soporte incluido</span>
                  <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground bg-secondary px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md">PC, tablet y celular</span>
                  <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground bg-secondary px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md">Personalizado</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="group bg-card border border-border rounded-xl p-6 md:p-7 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-black/[0.02] hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/><line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-1.5">P&aacute;ginas web para tu negocio</h3>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
                  Tu negocio merece estar en internet. Te creo una p&aacute;gina donde tus clientes
                  encuentran tus servicios, horarios, ubicaci&oacute;n y pueden contactarte directo.
                  Se ve bien en cualquier dispositivo. Pago &uacute;nico y es tuya.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
                  <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground bg-secondary px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md">Pago &uacute;nico</span>
                  <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground bg-secondary px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md">Dise&ntilde;o profesional</span>
                  <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground bg-secondary px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md">Adaptable a celulares</span>
                  <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground bg-secondary px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md">WhatsApp integrado</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="group bg-card border border-border rounded-xl p-6 md:p-7 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-black/[0.02] hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <path d="M12 2a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v1a4 4 0 0 0-4 4 4 4 0 0 0 4 4h1v3a4 4 0 0 0 8 0v-3h1a4 4 0 0 0 4-4 4 4 0 0 0-4-4V6a4 4 0 0 0-4-4z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-1.5">Automatizaciones con IA</h3>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
                  Esas tareas que haces todos los d&iacute;as y te aburren o te quitan tiempo:
                  responder mensajes, organizar datos, generar reportes, dar seguimiento a clientes.
                  La IA puede hacerlas por ti. Se maneja con pago mensual y soporte continuo.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
                  <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground bg-secondary px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md">Pago mensual</span>
                  <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground bg-secondary px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md">Tareas repetitivas</span>
                  <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground bg-secondary px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md">Respuestas autom&aacute;ticas</span>
                  <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground bg-secondary px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md">Soporte incluido</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="group bg-card border border-border rounded-xl p-6 md:p-7 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-black/[0.02] hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-1.5">Entrevista para tu negocio</h3>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
                  Agendamos una pl&aacute;tica sin ning&uacute;n compromiso. Me cuentas c&oacute;mo trabajas,
                  qu&eacute; te quita tiempo, qu&eacute; tareas odias hacer, qu&eacute; problemas tienes con tu
                  sistema actual. De ah&iacute; vemos si puedo ayudarte.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
                  <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground bg-secondary px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md">Sin costo</span>
                  <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground bg-secondary px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md">Sin compromiso</span>
                  <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground bg-secondary px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md">Presencial o remoto</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Section - Local Expertise -->
    <section id="about" class="py-20 md:py-28 px-6 bg-card border-t border-border">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-20 items-start">
          <div>
            <p class="badge text-accent mb-4">C&oacute;mo trabajo</p>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-balance mb-6">
              Primero te escucho, luego te propongo algo &uacute;til
            </h2>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-8 text-sm md:text-base">
              Vivo en Cd. Victoria y conozco el d&iacute;a a d&iacute;a de los negocios locales.
              No te voy a vender tecnolog&iacute;a que no necesitas. Primero nos tomamos un caf&eacute;
              o una videollamada, identificamos d&oacute;nde pierdes tiempo y dinero, y de ah&iacute;
              partimos para construir la soluci&oacute;n justa para ti.
            </p>

            <div class="space-y-5">
              <div class="flex gap-4 group">
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                  <span class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center text-accent text-xs font-semibold flex-shrink-0">1</span>
                  <div class="w-px flex-1 bg-border mt-2 group-last:hidden"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="pb-5 group-last:pb-0">
                  <h4 class="font-medium text-sm text-foreground mb-0.5">Agendamos una pl&aacute;tica</h4>
                  <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed">Sin costo, sin compromiso. Me cuentas c&oacute;mo funciona tu negocio y qu&eacute; te gustar&iacute;a mejorar o qu&eacute; tareas odias hacer.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex gap-4 group">
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                  <span class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center text-accent text-xs font-semibold flex-shrink-0">2</span>
                  <div class="w-px flex-1 bg-border mt-2 group-last:hidden"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="pb-5 group-last:pb-0">
                  <h4 class="font-medium text-sm text-foreground mb-0.5">Propongo una soluci&oacute;n concreta</h4>
                  <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed">Te explico qu&eacute; puedo hacer, cu&aacute;nto tiempo tomar&iacute;a y qu&eacute; costo tiene. Sin tecnicismos raros ni promesas falsas.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex gap-4 group">
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                  <span class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center text-accent text-xs font-semibold flex-shrink-0">3</span>
                  <div class="w-px flex-1 bg-border mt-2 group-last:hidden"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="pb-5 group-last:pb-0">
                  <h4 class="font-medium text-sm text-foreground mb-0.5">Construyo y entrego</h4>
                  <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed">Desarrollo tu sistema, web o automatizaci&oacute;n. Te explico c&oacute;mo usarlo y queda funcionando.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex gap-4 group">
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                  <span class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center text-accent text-xs font-semibold flex-shrink-0">4</span>
                  <div class="w-px flex-1 bg-border mt-2 group-last:hidden"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="pb-5 group-last:pb-0">
                  <h4 class="font-medium text-sm text-foreground mb-0.5">Precios claros desde el inicio</h4>
                  <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed">Cosas sencillas como una pagina web informativa se pagan una sola vez. Sistemas complejos o automatizaciones se manejan con pago mensual y soporte incluido.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <div class="bg-background border border-border rounded-2xl p-7 md:p-8 relative">
              <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 w-16 h-16 bg-accent/5 rounded-full blur-xl -z-10"></div>
              
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6 pb-6 border-b border-border">
                <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-full bg-accent flex items-center justify-center text-white text-sm font-semibold">N</div>
                <div>
                  <div class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground">Nexova</div>
                  <div class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">Cd. Victoria, Tamaulipas</div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-5">
                <div class="flex gap-3">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"/><path d="M12 9v4"/><path d="M10 11h4"/></svg>
                  <div>
                    <div class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground">Soluciones locales</div>
                    <div class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">Desarrollado en Cd. Victoria para negocios de la regi&oacute;n</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-3">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <div>
                    <div class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground">A tu medida</div>
                    <div class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">Cada negocio es &uacute;nico, como las calles de Cd. Victoria</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-3">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
                  <div>
                    <div class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground">Precios justos</div>
                    <div class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">Pago &uacute;nico o mensual seg&uacute;n el proyecto</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-3">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"/><path d="M12 17h.01"/></svg>
                  <div>
                    <div class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground">Asesor&iacute;a gratuita</div>
                    <div class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">Aunque no compres, te ayudo a elegir lo mejor</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <ContactForm client:load />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
